              Double Pendulum Simulation
            </h3>
            
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Interactive double pendulum demonstrating chaotic behavior and sensitive dependence on initial conditions
            </p>
            
            <div class="mt-4">
              <a href="/math/double-pendulum" class="inline-block bg-white/20 hover:bg-white/30 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded border border-white/30 transition-colors text-sm">
